-- Harmony Gold Reserves Are Steady at 48 Million Ounces in Latest Statement
-- Alastair Reed
-- 2010-08-02T13:59:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-08-02/harmony-gold-reserves-are-steady-at-48-million-ounces-in-latest-statement.html

          
          
             Harmony Gold Mining Ltd. said it
maintained its reserves of the metal at 48 million ounces in its
latest Statement of Mineral Resources and Mineral Reserves.  
          
          


  


        